                        <provenance>
                            <p>The manuscripts <ref target="#Acc-0051-en #Acc-0052-en #Acc-0053-en #Acc-0054-en #Acc-0055-en #Acc-0056-en                                  #Acc-0058-en #Acc-0059-en #Acc-0060-en #Acc-0061-en #Acc-0062-en">Acc. 51-62</ref> belong to the collection of manuscripts
                                Frederik Schaldemose bequeathed to <name type="org">Nykøbing
                                    Katedralskole</name>. Most of them are Fredrik Schaldemose's
